# Alpha Hunter v6 — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get your key: https://console.anthropic.com → API Keys → Create Key
#
# PAY-PER-USE PRICING (as of 2025):
#   claude-sonnet-4-20250514: $3 per 1M input tokens / $15 per 1M output tokens
#   Typical costs:
#     - AI Analysis button:    ~$0.01-0.02 per click
#     - Trade Setups full scan: ~$0.10-0.30 (15 stocks × web search)
#     - AI Scanner question:   ~$0.01-0.03 per query
#     - Trade Signal:          ~$0.01-0.02 per signal
#   Estimated daily cost for active use: $0.50 - $2.00
